# Images Directory

This directory is for site images. Recommended structure:

/images/
  ├── og-image.jpg          # OpenGraph social sharing (1200x630px)
  ├── apple-touch-icon.png  # iOS home screen icon (180x180px)
  └── community/            # Community service photos
      ├── outreach-1.jpg
      ├── outreach-2.jpg
      └── ...

Image Guidelines:
- Optimize all images for web before uploading
- Use descriptive filenames (e.g., "care-package-assembly.jpg")
- Recommended formats: WebP, JPEG, PNG
- Update alt text in HTML when adding images
